IN DEBIAN LIKE SYSTEMS

Installing : 
  $ sudo apt-get install apache2

Start server :
  $ sudo service apache2 start

Check status of server :
  $ sudo service apache2 status

Stop the server :
  $ sudo service apache2 stop

Upload html files to server :
 -> change directory to /var/www/html
  $ cd /var/www/html
 -> create your html files
  $ sudo vi index.html

Check if you can see uploade html is visible in your browser : 
  Type this in URL : 127.0.0.1:80
